<li>Action mode for uploads</li>
<li>The picture view was changed</li>
<li>The file editor was changed</li>
<ul>
<li>UNDO/REDO functions (BETA)</li>
<li>Line numbers (BETA)</li>
</ul>
<li>Progress bar when deleting files</li>
<li>Now you can hide the download/upload dialog</li>
